Setup an Official Windows 10 VM in Under 10 Minutes
Open a browser and navigate to https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/tools/vms/
Select VirtualBox from the platform options
Extract the downloaded .zip file
Launch VirtualBox
Select File > Import Appliance...
Click the Browse icon > Navigate to the extracted files .ova file > Select MSEdge - Win10.ova
Click Next and then Import
Make sure the MSEdge - Win10 VM is selected and click Start > Normal
That's it
